.SH TROUBLESHOOTING
.TP
.B GUI won't start
Install python3-customtkinter:
.br
  $ sudo apt install python3-customtkinter
.br
Test tkinter installation:
.br
  $ python3 -m tkinter
.TP
.B Backend won't start from GUI
1. Verify script path in Settings tab points to borednomore3.py
.br
2. Check python3 is in PATH: which python3
.br
3. Enable Debug Mode and check console for errors
.TP
.B Console shows no output
Enable Debug Mode checkbox (-D flag) for detailed logging from backend
.TP
.B Process won't stop
1. Click FORCE KILL button
.br
2. Click "Cleanup Processes" button
.br
3. Manually: pkill -9 -f borednomore3.py
.TP
.B GUI freezes or becomes unresponsive
Force close and check for zombie processes:
.br
  $ ps aux | grep borednomore3
.br
  $ pkill -9 -f borednomore3
.TP
.B State file corrupted
Delete and restart:
.br
  $ rm ~/.config/borednomore3/.bnm3_gui_state.json
.br
  $ bnm3
